                <td bgcolor="#333366" valign="top"><font color="white" face="Verdana" size="2"><small>Posted&nbsp;-&nbsp;11/20/2002&nbsp;: 10:49:44 AM</small><hr size="2"><span class="spnMessageText"> QUESTION:<br /><br />I heard that lower Charisma will make my Fears less resistable.  Is this true?<br /><br />ANSWER:<br /><br />No, it's not.  You will encounter people who swear up and down that it does, but don't listen to them.  Negative Charisma on stats is generally for RP purposes and will only affect your price with merchants.  Verant has said this.  <br /><br />Anytime someone doesn't believe you, remind them that the Necromancer epic weapon has POSITIVE Charisma.  Say what you will about VI, they're not going to put a statistic on an epic that's going to CRIPPLE your effectiveness.  That generally ends the argument.</span></font></td>
              </tr>
